Beatrice Kay https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Beatrice_Kay 0 Beatrice Kay (April 21, 1907 in New York City – November 8, 1986) was an American singer, vaudevillian, music hall performer, stage and film actress. She died in North Hollywood, California, aged 79.
